{
  "stem": "15991.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But at the time, there was very little talk about religion, though.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It meant we're just like everybody else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it really didn't mean very much to me, I'm sorry to say, because, simply because there was no religion in, in our household.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were-- the important thing was to be a good human being.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Paternal, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Both were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My maternal grandmother, I think, came from a very religious household.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think she was born in Denmark.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there was very little talk about that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I know very little about it, nothing really.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It did when I was about eight, nine-- nine years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And simply because I had a girlfriend who lived in the same floor we did in our apartment building.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was Christian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were a large family of lovely people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they moved away into the suburbs of Hamburg and [GERMAN] And when I visited there once, several times, I became very much aware of that I was somehow different than they were.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For one thing, their servants all commented on the wonderful hair I had, which was totally different than my friends, who was very blonde and had straight hair.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And mine was extremely curly and dark brown.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was wondering at that point why was she pointing out my hair so?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What were-- why was it so different?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'd never thought of it before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And later on, I realized why she had done that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a lot of talk at the dinner table about Jews and Christians, so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the worst of it was that in the neighborhood there was a group of teenage boys.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
